<p style="line-height:1.295;margin-bottom:8pt;margin-top:0pt;" dir="ltr"><span style="background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;font-size:13pt;"><span style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Lighting is just as important in the kitchen. Under-cabinet lighting makes tasks like chopping vegetables or reading recipes easier. Additionally, ensure the flooring is slip-resistant to provide stability while standing for extended periods.</span></span></p>
