<p style="line-height:1.295;margin-bottom:8pt;margin-top:0pt;" dir="ltr"><span style="background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;font-size:13pt;"><span style="font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">The right home modifications can do more than prevent accidents—they can transform your living space into a haven of comfort and support. Whether you’re starting small with a few quick fixes or planning major renovations, the changes you make today will have a lasting impact on your quality of life.</span></span></p>
