    title: "Affordable and practical home improvement solutions for seniors",
    description:
      "Making a home safe and comfortable for seniors doesn’t have to cost a fortune. Small changes like adding grab bars in the bathroom, swapping out slippery rugs for non-slip mats, or installing motion-sensor lights can make a big difference. Even simple updates like lever-style door handles or rearranging furniture to create clear pathways can make daily life so much easier. These upgrades aren’t just practical—they’re empowering, helping seniors stay independent and confident in their own homes. And let’s be honest, peace of mind for the family? That’s priceless.",
    Icon: MovingIcon,
